{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_M_Punch}}
'''A_M_Punch''' (int ''force'')<br>

Does nothing if the calling actor has no valid target.

Otherwise, calls [[A_FaceTarget]], then performs a melee-range hitscan attack with a horizontal spread of 5.625Â° that inflicts ''force'' times 2d10 melee damage to the target and spawns a {{Class|BulletPuff}}, and finally plays the sound "*fist" on the WEAPON channel. Using a ''force'' of 1 replicates the effect of a normal {{Class|Fist}} [[A_Punch|punch]], with a ''force'' of 10 it replicates the effect of a {{Class|Berserk}} punch.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|ScriptedMarine}} and derived classes.

